maintext:
SPRINGFIELD, Ill. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Illinois Lottery’s “LuckyDay Lotto Midday” game were:
08-18-19-23-28
(eight, eighteen, nineteen, twenty-three, twenty-eight)
